{"title":"Insuficiencia respiratoria aguda-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Nefrología/Insuficiencia respiratoria aguda-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Insuficiencia\\Nrespiratoria aguda","guid":"OAcbrRfPt38YwSBMPNOhQg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Perlas:","guid":"1euwlUUl3ieMlx1oe4bpfw","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Cuál es la definición de IRA?","guid":"vvoF1NurLRD7bXhLqZtf2Q","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Incapacidad del sistema respiratorio de mantener una adecuada oxigenación y/o ventilación.","guid":"3ob3zFxdroHHT8tuqq1wEg","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Cuáles son los tipos de IRA?","guid":"tHvO4-L6os2UTLT_-j-p-A","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Hipoxémica (tipo 1) e hipercápnica (tipo 2).","guid":"miXQKb_wOGaGlW2XktpTkw","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Cuál es la principal causa de IRA hipoxémica?","guid":"u3EMEG2r4bb4PBsSiFu4oQ","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"Alteración de la relación ventilación/perfusión (V/Q).","guid":"Gf7l8TXHLzpqWFZ7r2Qczw","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Cuál es el objetivo terapéutico en IRA?","guid":"sqne3HQc7JIdVt6DPbxaPQ","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"Mantener una adecuada oxigenación y ventilación, tratando la causa subyacente.","guid":"Qb-KdDEaLoc7_OoDvkexUA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"0","text":"Fisiología del\\Nintercambio gaseoso","guid":"w1y1AD5cC3HDQF_7y9aBYQ","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"- La respiración normal implica un adecuado intercambio gaseoso, con una relación V/Q óptima.","guid":"Fwl-hNwr69cp10NJ7Kx45g","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"Presión\\Natmosférica (Pb)","guid":"RvwSoLONSTcHTRNeQPq4_w","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"aire: 21% O2, 79% N2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"↓Pb por ↑altitud → ↓PaO2","guid":"nDi7HEq2yyCdkfzUa3eocQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"Ecuación del\\Ngas alveolar","guid":"6rAlEOWppcZV9HC5WULoyA","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"PAO2 = (Pb - PH2O) FiO2 - PaCO2/R","guid":"CTfh4PfJbRjrUeG-WeUKnw","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"R = VCO2/VO2 ≈ 0.8","guid":"StOrMxiRCBBsWXBp9Zk93w","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"15","text":"Gradiente alvéolo-arterial de O2 (AaO2) = PAO2 - PaO2","guid":"6njiclhAWQXk8Alew2oQDQ","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"15","text":"AaO2 normal: 2.5 + (0.21 x edad) (1)","guid":"F1tEyXRZMjGShp8IlA2egA","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"10","text":"Difusión de gases\\N(Ley de Fick)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Depende de: gradiente de presión, área de superficie, grosor de membrana","guid":"x6iZUF2XWxKdZlBDMqixYg","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"O2: ↓solubilidad y ↑PM → difusión más lenta vs CO2 (2)","guid":"YdtZFeGb7Ria6h0W5WenFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"10","text":"Gradiente alvéolo-arterial de O2\\N(P(A-a)O2)","guid":"qv6bZ5PkdHCWObAkrSA-2w","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Normal: 5-10 mmHg (1)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"↑ por shunts anatómicos (circulación bronquial, coronaria, pleural)","guid":"kDY7qsQdmls3c0u6uVMCwg","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"10","text":"Transporte de\\NO2 en sangre","guid":"41OSUgt9AbMOyZpp6SyLyQ","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Disuelto: PaO2 x 0. 003 mL/dL/mmHg","guid":"kWIOK7ncsThfJ17TUnxcwg","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Unido a Hb: 1.34 mL/g Hb x SaO2","guid":"9mFoGEv68E3N6yzzu7BD-w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"0","text":"Mecanismos Fisiopatológicos\\Nde Hipoxemia","guid":"aUvYT9Y5hO9UqIEYwHOy0A","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"General","guid":"hctatX_sp8xYBPGv6CRH0w","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"- En IRA hipoxémica, la alteración de la relación V/Q es la causa principal, debido a shunt o desajuste V/Q (2).","guid":"daP5ie2k49ntnt8k_KK3uQ","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"- En IRA hipercápnica, la hipoventilación alveolar es el mecanismo fisiopatológico principal.","guid":"oBbb0BmBNE09gm4tdiZhkw","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"- Los objetivos terapéuticos son mantener una adecuada oxigenación \\N(PaO2 > 60 mmHg, SaO2 > 90%) y ventilación (PaCO2 < 45 mmHg, pH > 7.35) (3).","guid":"DFIB-Lhar6oOLFpFiW-JEQ","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"30","text":"- La investigación futura podría enfocarse en nuevas estrategias de\\Nventilación y tratamientos específicos para las causas subyacentes.","guid":"VjQ7ALeGSPyllU1csdmAxw","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"29","text":"Hipoventilación alveolar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"↓VA → ↑PaCO2 → ↓PAO2 → ↓PaO2","guid":"cciFeR_FsxFeUjzbcmWYiw","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"29","text":"Alteración de\\Nla difusión","guid":"8VQiyHusmTr6lMdmzqcrvw","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Causas: EPD, EPOC, HAP, HAD","guid":"YoJPi1RET2gu19IDiYUqjA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"Hipoxemia inicial solo durante ejercicio","guid":"6hIunwKYZyKN6kHg7Y3gog","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"Hipercapnia en etapas avanzadas","guid":"2Qqyspu9UHay9_gdEDgbQg","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"29","text":"Alteración de la relación\\Nventilación/perfusión (V/Q)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Espectro de V/Q de West (3)","guid":"OnuA6-xQqftAe_e9oj5h2g","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"V/Q = 0 (shunt) → ↓PaO2","guid":"2pbc4TgBlp15wnpxC6sxQQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"V/Q = ∞ (espacio muerto) → ↑PaCO2","guid":"7lnBVgugWL2y5Fh38HbwQA","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"41","text":"V/Q = 0.1-10 (desajuste V/Q) → ↓PaO2, ↑PaCO2","guid":"SOooyeQvyAAGCfmmK0A_pw","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"29","text":"Shunt pulmonar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Fracción de shunt (Qs/Qt)","guid":"54W4E1hd4ZPYUEsyOjAxCw","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Normal <5% (4)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"↑Qs/Qt → ↓PaO2 (refractaria a ↑FiO2)","guid":"eRAZFmoFjsRgva0QE5usKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"29","text":"Mecanismos\\Nfisiopatológicos de\\Nhipoxemia","guid":"KMPDcmZ2zjO10-MbJRO5-w","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"Hipoventilación alveolar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"↓VA → ↑PaCO2 → ↓PAO2 → ↓PaO2","guid":"Gq-oGpIYJAw0GVHrJXiGNQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"Alteración de la difusión","guid":"","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Causas: Enf. pulmonar difusa,\\Nedema, enfisema, atelectasia,\\Ncontusión, hemorragia, HAP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"Hipoxemia inicial\\Nsolo en ejercicio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"53","text":"Hipercapnia en\\Netapas avanzadas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"50","text":"Alteración de la\\Nrelación V/Q","guid":"","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Causa más común\\Nde hipoxemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"Hipercapnia leve","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"↑AaO2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"Hipoxemia mejora\\Ncon ejercicio","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"50","text":"Shunt pulmonar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"Hipoxemia\\Nrefractaria a O2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"Demostrable con\\NFiO2 100%","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"29","text":"Patrones de gases arteriales\\Nsegún mecanismo (3)","guid":"fg0EHHGPLolBJKGGgCwb1g","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"A: Hipoventilación Alveolar","guid":"vKRmvYiSd07Rz7ABxjVnYA","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"B: Alteración V/Q","guid":"CMny_0nls3TSHKwR_Ia4Cg","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"C: Alteración de la Difusión","guid":"re_u28p6ueSzOrr6p_uM5Q","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"65","text":"D: Shunt Pulmonar","guid":"ZAQCPbuXDWDkt6p9n5tIuw","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"65","text":"E: VMI en Shunt","guid":"lPmzSgaxef0XBnG9IFYz6g","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"65","text":"F: O2 en IRA crónica","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"0","text":"Definición","guid":"YpMUfNcLA6tJ71a38ffmVg","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Alteración grave del intercambio gaseoso","guid":"i9RIc3eOMq4hGGOa424MNQ","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Resultado de múltiples mecanismos fisiopatológicos","guid":"nspG3_G8A-sJZ_ZD7IgohA","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"- La IRA se define como la incapacidad del sistema respiratorio de mantener una adecuada oxigenación\\N(PaO2 < 60 mmHg) y/o ventilación (PaCO2 > 45 mmHg) (1).","guid":"l67L78MOTulMOb6r57olYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología:","guid":"CtfcNe1wtfi3Jn8dRLMiPg","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"- La IRA es una condición frecuente en unidades de cuidados intensivos (UCI), con una incidencia estimada del 30% (4).","guid":"w_OgwPzVtHi-UJs5HPT0vw","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"- En Chile, la IRA es una de las principales causas de ingreso a UCI, especialmente en pacientes geriátricos (5).","guid":"-DjN_PkyfWndp5cQ8X5Fkw","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"- La IRA se asocia con una alta morbilidad y mortalidad, llegando hasta un 40% en algunos estudios (6).","guid":"hxeT1zEIw8PkBK105_o2_g","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo:","guid":"Yd9Qz6zmgc87BMcIUUgZoA","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"- Edad avanzada (RR: 2.5)","guid":"rzFDpiM3tFjKKLOotMT9fg","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"- Enfermedad pulmonar crónica (RR: 3.2)","guid":"0IFmvA9ZMaA3HvGZ24oRRQ","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"- Inmunosupresión (RR: 2.8)","guid":"71Eb6vfBZImnG155WCoGiQ","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"80","text":"- Cirugía torácica o abdominal (RR: 2.1) (7)","guid":"FH9dA1eC3slJFNabJ84RRw","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"0","text":"Causas:","guid":"4_a-LWWe05_DvBFniIx6uA","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"- Neumonía (40%)","guid":"QkxxqiX1ov5GZOUEUqS28Q","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"- Enfermedad pulmonar obstructiva crónica (EPOC) exacerbada (25%)","guid":"Z_aPBeu5dtMfYUsZQTlfYg","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"- Edema pulmonar cardiogénico (15%)","guid":"oyiTjQhB8EncraojUgurCg","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"- Síndrome de distrés respiratorio agudo (SDRA) (10%)","guid":"n-0hTKcHpOXNLbbvr7xCGQ","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"- Otras (10%)","guid":"-tfyU3qO_TnIz8-D0cHAxg","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"- Neumotórax","guid":"_XEvWZ0oJuO9Lvi-9eq6eg","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"- Embolia pulmonar","guid":"2xudgW6Ygm16ld89G73iHg","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"- Atelectasia masiva","guid":"fwxKTgdHKh9-oo5tpmirQQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"0","text":"Clínica:","guid":"ZwxrcBC2WUp_CfKXYcn1zw","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"- Antecedentes: enfermedad pulmonar crónica, inmunosupresión, cirugía reciente.","guid":"jr25cdP3LVIYzvzR1-6inQ","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"94","text":"- Cuadro clínico:","guid":"wBwmJ5SgXd6sGl1QVUCk2A","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"- Disnea (OR: 5.6)","guid":"w1AtkNBuoDERURirnYSVVQ","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"- Taquipnea (> 30 rpm) (OR: 4.2)","guid":"crWzmxPapcFs51xgEm8QJw","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"- Uso de musculatura accesoria (OR: 3.8)","guid":"GXrO2OT3MDUkLrGn1T8reA","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"96","text":"- Cianosis (OR: 3.1)","guid":"ZXmem-V7aViwTigghYQ4uA","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"96","text":"- Alteración del estado mental (OR: 2.7) (8)","guid":"jqyUsCG9vVbba5Cy_JLXpw","children":[]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"94","text":"- Triada de IRA: disnea, taquipnea e hipoxemia.","guid":"PM3aXyts7r6IoYINHun02A","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"94","text":"- Factores de mal pronóstico: edad avanzada, comorbilidades, SDRA, shock.","guid":"6lQx4oAX4TtOmaWiKIMARw","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"94","text":"- Complicaciones: insuficiencia multiorgánica, neumonía asociada a ventilación mecánica (NAVM).","guid":"pb85ZIOyoaDO8TLcw02fqg","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"0","text":"Estudio:","guid":"i9S1Js1YMYxWdJDr7kqd8w","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"- Gases arteriales: PaO2 < 60 mmHg, PaCO2 > 45 mmHg (LR+: 5.2)","guid":"UG8s7ySSKyNLxAwagXLQQg","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"- Radiografía de tórax: infiltrados, atelectasias, neumotórax (LR+: 3.5)","guid":"Oi4wI1Xp4uzGQXwJj1PmKQ","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"- Hemograma: leucocitosis o leucopenia (LR+: 2.1)","guid":"RnN3vCToyW3EbNslHh1aWA","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"- Procalcitonina elevada en caso de infección (LR+: 4.8) (9)","guid":"ZjCJNNkblGxAMPZHZ4Yg3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"0","text":"Scores:","guid":"4RoFyww5Vtu5oRdrir1Zzg","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"- Índice de Murray (LIS): evalúa la gravedad del SDRA (OR: 3.2 para mortalidad con LIS > 2.5) (10)","guid":"5thxtC8ZC4p5dPOaxcCUFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos\\Ndiferenciales:","guid":"dsX7CxfVvqTAz5DqufDK7w","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"- Síndrome de disnea aguda","guid":"dOJsmFvGNNjN_oYBk0K4IA","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"- Insuficiencia cardíaca descompensada","guid":"yiEzy5tbQHXJRO5KPqdEeg","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"- Tromboembolismo pulmonar","guid":"_AER5S396-T2NmbtnUWISg","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"- Crisis asmática","guid":"BNMLIiP9H_N4aIenirLVzA","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"112","text":"- Obstrucción de vía aérea superior","guid":"Uw5Q3OpvGgM3vYMcYoc0nQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"0","text":"Tamizaje:","guid":"VZ0p0O-tW09eov5jGLxzLA","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"- Oximetría de pulso: SaO2 < 90%\\N(sensibilidad: 80%, especificidad: 90%) (13)","guid":"n34jpwQpAI9Dyjso0I-_lw","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"bj1Ur7EN-MDq4srp8IoCUA","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"- Diagnóstico sindrómico: IRA","guid":"f-9FP-77MCB2CoEhDSOPaQ","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"- Clasificación: IRA hipoxémica (tipo 1) e hipercápnica (tipo 2)","guid":"woTAiQWRm26jV086CmRaFQ","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"120","text":"- Gold standard: gases arteriales (sensibilidad: 95%, especificidad: 90%) (11)","guid":"oZXPwyenz4ubmRgCT-85Gg","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"- Criterios diagnósticos: PaO2 < 60 mmHg y/o PaCO2 > 45 mmHg","guid":"sHm0IdJHo0kFKf4h_RDyuA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"-gods8mpW2b6iL0CMpwSjw","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"- Objetivo: mantener una adecuada oxigenación y ventilación, tratando la causa subyacente.","guid":"D-qGIo5tt5Gjw5a-3AqqvQ","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"- No farmacológico:","guid":"wT4mbeYF1N3aJokkfTUyZw","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"- Oxigenoterapia\\N(primera línea)","guid":"mbnGvVV-8psgK8qqfVAEhA","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"- Cánula nasal: 1-5 L/min","guid":"Wh0V7OxL5t9kjO6Djbxz_Q","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"- Mascarilla simple: 5-10 L/min","guid":"X0lS-pV6O8UAUl5ZErS46Q","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"- Mascarilla con reservorio: 10-15 L/min","guid":"JLuUSkYW1oOi9B3cYQZxEw","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"127","text":"- Ventilación mecánica no invasiva\\N(segunda línea)","guid":"IuMplkXKKGDXiXJqY0obcw","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"- CPAP: 5-20 cmH2O","guid":"NaiMxehH3RM-xoUP4iHsJQ","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"- BiPAP: IPAP 10-20 cmH2O, EPAP 5-10 cmH2O","guid":"UBJC3bTdG9Q81YtHaMUsAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"127","text":"- Ventilación mecánica invasiva\\N(tercera línea)","guid":"AFPmJBD5HFRhMHyqU1Q7MA","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"- Modos: controlado por volumen o presión","guid":"x0ozIY_CcW4BK1jMAnRpwQ","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"- Parámetros: VT 6-8 ml/kg, FR 12-20 rpm, PEEP 5-15 cmH2O","guid":"JDF9RM7DEuY5UdyyuEwvrQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"125","text":"- Farmacológico (según\\Ncausa subyacente):","guid":"B41mIMncOj2l-4hcTIoVmA","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"- Antibióticos en caso de neumonía","guid":"E9clxcbrtz2y-0K1qmMYNQ","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"- Broncodilatadores y corticoides en EPOC exacerbado","guid":"0Ghp3-by2Ig2sRQWECdxIw","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"138","text":"- Diuréticos en edema pulmonar cardiogénico","guid":"g0Sf9zRCBV9itZ_h589QmA","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"125","text":"- Efectos adversos: barotrauma, volutrauma, toxicidad por oxígeno.","guid":"oc4iLP-kR2oEIovZ72L98A","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"125","text":"- Interacciones: sedantes y relajantes musculares pueden prolongar la ventilación mecánica.","guid":"kqVYCTFd_7arSi8lHfbEeQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y\\Npronóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"- Escala APACHE II: evalúa la gravedad y predice la mortalidad en UCI\\N(OR: 2.8 para mortalidad con APACHE II > 20) (12)","guid":"EYr5UmGEF2DjQJP4ma_Vbw","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"- Seguimiento con gases arteriales,\\Nradiografía de tórax y mecánica respiratoria.","guid":"SxiFeT2N9wKXFLUGGFJp7Q","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"- Otros profesionales: kinesiólogo, nutricionista, infectólogo.","guid":"mamVZZAlUyE_QBMbwJQpOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"0","text":"Prevención:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"- Vacunación contra influenza y neumococo en población de riesgo.","guid":"7AU1EutsDaiqPAtMpBHfnA","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"- Cesación tabáquica.","guid":"Top2hxybe3BebWU0x5u3Fw","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"- Manejo adecuado de enfermedades crónicas (EPOC, insuficiencia cardíaca).","guid":"_kzGKz4mxaP30-77Myp4Sw","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"0","text":"Aspectos Geriátricos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"- Mayor riesgo de IRA por comorbilidades y cambios fisiológicos del envejecimiento.","guid":"2e80bkxRO6eTgC8Q3Fhgrw","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"- Presentación atípica: delirio, deterioro funcional.","guid":"7M5ApACfHLmGG27DgszWDw","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"- Mayor riesgo de complicaciones y mortalidad.","guid":"A8LYEVxaoGNK9_S05R6WJw","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"aVVp3n25hij5XJ12Ix2GBw","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"1. Barbas CSV et al. Acute respiratory failure. Lancet. 2016; 388(10058):2416-2430.","guid":"MYmItIrdHPQC6zCWzAOE-w","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"2. West JB. Respiratory physiology: the essentials. 10th ed. Philadelphia: Wolters Kluwer; 2016.","guid":"tE_1qDjcQb9ai06Z15whog","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"156","text":"3. Papazian L et al. Formal guidelines: management of acute respiratory distress syndrome. Ann Intensive Care. 2019;9(1):69.","guid":"dAxB9a1TtDCrrgiILkoe_A","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"156","text":"4. Bellani G et al. Epidemiology, patterns of care, and mortality for patients with acute respiratory distress syndrome in intensive care units in 50 countries. JAMA. 20